translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: if (tt[cゼス３の移動先]==1)　ナガールモール周辺です、と地図で現在地表示
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: if (tt[cZes3Destination]==1) Display 'Around Nagarl Mall' and show current location on the map

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: if (tt[cゼス３の移動先]==2)　スリミド周辺です、と地図で現在地表示
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: if (tt[cZes3Destination]==2) Display 'Around Surimido' and show current location on the map

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: if (tt[cゼス３の移動先]==3)　イタリア周辺です、と地図で現在地表示
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: if (tt[cZes3Destination]==3) Display 'Around Italia' and show current location on the map

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 気をつけて下さい、すでに魔軍の支配地の中です。数万の魔軍がこの付近に展開しています
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Be careful, you are already inside the territory controlled by the Demon Army. Tens of thousands of demons are deployed around here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この暗闇に紛れて、いっきに攻め込むぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let's take advantage of this darkness and launch an all-out attack.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 狙いは魔物大将軍ツォトンだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Our target is the Demon General Tsoton.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ツォトンが確実にここにいるという保証はありませんよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There is no guarantee that Tsoton is definitely here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ふふふ、俺がここと選んだのだ、居るはずだ。確信
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hehe, I chose this place myself; he must be here. I'm certain.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ごー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Go!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 場面変わって・・・ゼスのどこかにある魔軍の司令部（場所はわからない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Scene change... The Demon Army's headquarters somewhere in Zes (location unknown).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ツォトンとその部下達の様子
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Tsoton and his subordinates' situation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: メディウサ、ガルティアを失ったが、魔物大将軍ツォトン率いる魔軍はまだまだ健在
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They lost Medusa and Galtia, but the Demon Army led by General Tsoton is still strong.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これまでの戦いでゼス本土の５割は支配しており、少し時間はかかるがいずれは
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: So far in the battles, they have controlled half of the Zes mainland; it will take some time but eventually...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 全土を支配出来るというつもりでいる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They intend to conquer the entire land.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 偉そうな魔人がいなくなって逆にやりやすいとすら思っている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They even think it's easier without the arrogant demon lords around.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私は私の思想で理想的に人間共を管理したいのだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I want to manage the humans ideally according to my own ideology.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 計画通り進めておるな、ポルよ。＜＝魔物将軍、イメージ＝ポルポト
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The plan is progressing as intended, Pol. <= Demon General, image = Pol Pot

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリス様は各方面の人類を８割減らし、２割を飼い慣らせと命じられた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lord Keblis commanded to reduce humanity in all areas by 80% and tame the remaining 20%.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だが、それは無駄に恐れすぎだ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, that is an unnecessary over-fear,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それでは我々の為に働く労働力や、我々の娯楽となる者がいなくなる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If so, there will be no workforce to serve us or those who entertain us.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ただ単に殺せば良いというものでは無い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You can't just kill them indiscriminately.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一時的な間引きより、時間がかかっても良いが何世代に渡っても管理しやすいようする事が大事だ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rather than a temporary thinning out, it's important to manage them in a sustainable way over generations, even if it takes longer.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私は人間の数をあまり減らさずに理想的な支配を実現させる自信があるのだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I am confident that I can achieve ideal control without drastically reducing the human population.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何度か魔軍とは戦闘したが、敵の本体というか魔物大将軍ツォトンは見つからなかった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We fought the Demon Army several times but could not find the enemy's main body, or the Demon General Tsoton.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いや、ツォトンどこから魔物将軍すら接触出来ない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, Tsoton is unreachable even by the Demon Generals.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: くっ・・見つからんな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Damn... can't find him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 闇雲に突撃しても厳しいですね。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Charging blindly is tough, isn't it?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うむむ、なんか、ここにいそうな気がしたのだが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, I had a feeling he was around here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いや、あっちだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, over there.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 待って下さい、光蝕の日が始まって、もう２時間ほど立っています。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Please wait, the Day of Light Eclipse started about two hours ago.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そろそろ、星明かりも無くなる真っ暗となります、歩く事すら危険になるので
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Soon, the starlight will disappear and it will become pitch dark; walking will even be dangerous.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: このあたりでゼスの支配エリアに戻った方がよいですよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's better to return to the Zes controlled area around here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞選択
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Choice

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　戻る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Return

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　戻らない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Do not return

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 選択、戻るを選んだ時
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When choosing 'Return':

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しかたない、戻るか・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Can't be helped, let's go back...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そろそろ腹もへってきたしなとか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm getting hungry anyway.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 選択、戻らないを選んだ時
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When choosing 'Do not return':

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 真っ暗上等だ、そのまま捜すぞ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Bring on the pitch darkness, we'll keep searching.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺には　このスーパー忍者かなみがいる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I have this super ninja Kanami with me.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: かなみは、忍者だから夜でもまわりが見えるぞ、すごい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kanami is a ninja, so she can see her surroundings even at night, amazing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・・・えへ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Hehe.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ほんと？　光蝕の日、真っ暗になった時も？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Really? Even during the Day of Light Eclipse when it's pitch black?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: えっと・・それは・・見えないです
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Um... actually... I can't see then.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんだ、見えないのか役に立たない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What, you can't see? That's no help at all.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まぁいい、なんとかなる、いくぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, whatever, we'll manage. Let's go.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 背景の変化で真っ暗を表現
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Use background change to express pitch darkness.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おわっ、真っ暗だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Whoa, it's pitch dark.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィル、光だ・・魔法で光を出せ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sil, light... use magic to produce light.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔法が付くと立ち絵だけ見える感じにします。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When magic is activated, only the character sprites will be visible.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それでも暗いな、周囲がよく見えない。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Still it's dark; I can't see the surroundings well.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こういう時は・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At times like this...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 暗闇の隠れたランス・・誰かをさわる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance hidden in darkness... touches someone.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: きゃっ・・だれ・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kya... who...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: がははは・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Gahahaha...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もう遊んでいる場合ではないです
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We don't have time to play around anymore.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 暗いな・・よく見えない、いて・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's dark... can't see well, ouch...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あっ、すみませんと丁寧にわびる相手・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, sorry, I apologize politely to the person...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 気をつけて下さい、すでに魔軍の支配地の中です。数万の魔軍がこの付近に展開しています
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Be careful, you are already inside the territory controlled by the Demon Army. Tens of thousands of demons are deployed around here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この暗闇に紛れて、いっきに攻め込むぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let's take advantage of this darkness and launch an all-out attack.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 狙いは魔物大将軍ツォトンだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Our target is the Demon General Tsoton.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ツォトンが確実にここにいるという保証はありませんよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There is no guarantee that Tsoton is definitely here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ふふふ、俺がここと選んだのだ、居るはずだ。確信
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hehe, I chose this place myself; he must be here. I'm certain.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ごー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Go!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 場面変わって・・・ゼスのどこかにある魔軍の司令部（場所はわからない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Scene change... The Demon Army's headquarters somewhere in Zes (location unknown).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ツォトンとその部下達の様子
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Tsoton and his subordinates' situation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: メディウサ、ガルティアを失ったが、魔物大将軍ツォトン率いる魔軍はまだまだ健在
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They lost Medusa and Galtia, but the Demon Army led by General Tsoton is still strong.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これまでの戦いでゼス本土の５割は支配しており、少し時間はかかるがいずれは
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: So far in the battles, they have controlled half of the Zes mainland; it will take some time but eventually...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 全土を支配出来るというつもりでいる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They intend to conquer the entire land.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 偉そうな魔人がいなくなって逆にやりやすいとすら思っている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They even think it's easier without the arrogant demon lords around.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私は私の思想で理想的に人間共を管理したいのだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I want to manage the humans ideally according to my own ideology.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 計画通り進めておるな、ポルよ。＜＝魔物将軍、イメージ＝ポルポト
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The plan is progressing as intended, Pol. <= Demon General, image = Pol Pot

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリス様は各方面の人類を８割減らし、２割を飼い慣らせと命じられた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lord Keblis commanded to reduce humanity in all areas by 80% and tame the remaining 20%.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だが、それは無駄に恐れすぎだ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, that is an unnecessary over-fear,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それでは我々の為に働く労働力や、我々の娯楽となる者がいなくなる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If so, there will be no workforce to serve us or those who entertain us.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ただ単に殺せば良いというものでは無い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You can't just kill them indiscriminately.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一時的な間引きより、時間がかかっても良いが何世代に渡っても管理しやすいようする事が大事だ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rather than a temporary thinning out, it's important to manage them in a sustainable way over generations, even if it takes longer.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私は人間の数をあまり減らさずに理想的な支配を実現させる自信があるのだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I am confident that I can achieve ideal control without drastically reducing the human population.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何度か魔軍とは戦闘したが、敵の本体というか魔物大将軍ツォトンは見つからなかった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We fought the Demon Army several times but could not find the enemy's main body, or the Demon General Tsoton.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いや、ツォトンどこから魔物将軍すら接触出来ない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, Tsoton is unreachable even by the Demon Generals.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: くっ・・見つからんな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Damn... can't find him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 闇雲に突撃しても厳しいですね。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Charging blindly is tough, isn't it?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うむむ、なんか、ここにいそうな気がしたのだが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, I had a feeling he was around here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いや、あっちだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, over there.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 待って下さい、光蝕の日が始まって、もう２時間ほど立っています。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Please wait, the Day of Light Eclipse started about two hours ago.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そろそろ、星明かりも無くなる真っ暗となります、歩く事すら危険になるので
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Soon, the starlight will disappear and it will become pitch dark; walking will even be dangerous.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: このあたりでゼスの支配エリアに戻った方がよいですよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's better to return to the Zes controlled area around here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞選択
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Choice

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　戻る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Return

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　戻らない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Do not return

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 選択、戻るを選んだ時
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When choosing 'Return':

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しかたない、戻るか・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Can't be helped, let's go back...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そろそろ腹もへってきたしなとか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm getting hungry anyway.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 選択、戻らないを選んだ時
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When choosing 'Do not return':

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 真っ暗上等だ、そのまま捜すぞ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Bring on the pitch darkness, we'll keep searching.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺には　このスーパー忍者かなみがいる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I have this super ninja Kanami with me.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: かなみは、忍者だから夜でもまわりが見えるぞ、すごい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kanami is a ninja, so she can see her surroundings even at night, amazing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・・・えへ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Hehe.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ほんと？　光蝕の日、真っ暗になった時も？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Really? Even during the Day of Light Eclipse when it's pitch black?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: えっと・・それは・・見えないです
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Um... actually... I can't see then.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんだ、見えないのか役に立たない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What, you can't see? That's no help at all.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まぁいい、なんとかなる、いくぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, whatever, we'll manage. Let's go.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 背景の変化で真っ暗を表現
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Use background change to express pitch darkness.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おわっ、真っ暗だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Whoa, it's pitch dark.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィル、光だ・・魔法で光を出せ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sil, light... use magic to produce light.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔法が付くと立ち絵だけ見える感じにします。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When magic is activated, only the character sprites will be visible.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それでも暗いな、周囲がよく見えない。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Still it's dark; I can't see the surroundings well.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こういう時は・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At times like this...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 暗闇の隠れたランス・・誰かをさわる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance hidden in darkness... touches someone.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: きゃっ・・だれ・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kya... who...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: がははは・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Gahahaha...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もう遊んでいる場合ではないです
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We don't have time to play around anymore.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 暗いな・・よく見えない、いて・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's dark... can't see well, ouch...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あっ、すみませんと丁寧にわびる相手・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, sorry, I apologize politely to the person...
